<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <title>{% block title %}Zoo{% endblock %}</title>
        <link rel="icon" href="data:image/svg+xml,<svg xmlns=%22http://www.w3.org/2000/svg%22 viewBox=%220 0 128 128%22><text y=%221.2em%22 font-size=%2296%22>⚫️</text></svg>">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="scss/main.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
        {% block stylesheets %}
        {% endblock %}
    </head>
    <body>
    
    
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg bg-primary fixed-top">
            <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-space-between">
                <a class="navbar-brand text-white" href="#">Arcadia</a>
                <button class="navbar-toggler white" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                    <span class="navbar-toggler-icon text-white"></span>
                </button>
                <div class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end" id="navbarNav">
                    <ul class="navbar-nav ">
                        <li class="nav-item mx-3">
                            <a class="nav-link active text-white" aria-current="page" href="/home">Home</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item mx-3">
                            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="/services">Services</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item mx-3">
                            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="/habitats">Habitats</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item mx-3">
                            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="#">Connection</a>
                        </li>
                        <li class="nav-item mx-3">
                            <a class="nav-link text-white" href="/contact_us">Contact</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </nav>
        
        <div id="carouselExampleRide" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="true">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
            
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <div class="d-block slider-background  w-100">
                        <div class="text-white display-center">
                            <h1>Présentation du zoo</h1>
                            <h2>Welcome to our zoo</h1>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleRide" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExampleRide" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
        </div>
        

      
        
        {% block body %}{% endblock %}

        <!-- footer Section -->
        <div class="bg-primary py-4">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row text-white text-center">
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12 my-3">A zoo is a facility in which animals are kept within enclosures for 
                    public exhibition and often bred for conservation purposes. 
                    The term zoological garden refers to zoology, the study of animals</div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 text-center my-3">
                        Retrouvons-nous ici : </br>
                        <i class="bi bi-facebook fs-2" style="color:#AA1945"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-twitter fs-2" style="color:#AA1945"></i>
                        <i class="bi bi-tiktok fs-2" style="color:#AA1945"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-6 my-3">4 Rue des 3 Cailloux, </br> 80000 Amiens </br> lundi au samedi 9:00-17:00 </br> 03 22 11 33 098</div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        

        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

    </body>
</html>
